<h2> HOLLY JOLLY CHRISMAS </h2>

<h2 id="chord-progressions">Chord progressions</h2>

<p>Here are the three progressions youâ€™ll need in order to play this entire song. For the verse, note youâ€™ll bounce between the two progressions a few time before moving on to the chorus. See my video lesson for context where I play it through.</p>

<h3 id="verse">Verse</h3>

